[Whampoa Keng] - Dinner tonight is from one of my favourite Fish Head Steamboat restaurants. .
We ordered the following,

1. Our signature fish head steamboat soup (Batang Sliced Fish) 
2. Hotplate Nonya Sotong 
3. Sweet & Sour Pork Ribs with Crispy Cod 
4. Prawn Paste Chicken Wings
.
They are currently offering free island wide delivery daily for orders with a min spend of $50 and also 15% off for pick up orders. 
Order at Http://Whampoakeng.getz.co
